<P>__{(with trepidation)}
<D>__{yeah.}
<C>__{simple simon's voice}
<P>__{(building to crescendo)}
<D>__{trip? you just got yourself four tickets and four backstage passes to kiss live at cobo hall tonight!}
<A>__{pause.}
<C>__{trip's voice}
